@startuml
actor Client
participant "API Gateway (Traefik)" as Gateway
participant "Auth Service" as AuthService
participant "User Service" as UserService

== Case 1: Invalid/Missing Token ==

Client -> Gateway: GET /user/{userId}\nAuthorization: Bearer <invalid_token>
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthService: GET /auth\nAuthorization: Bearer <invalid_token>
activate AuthService
AuthService -> AuthService: Validate JWT Token
AuthService --> Gateway: 401 Unauthorized
deactivate AuthService

Gateway --> Client: 401 Unauthorized
deactivate Gateway

== Case 2: Mismatched User ID (Authorization Failure) ==

Client -> Gateway: GET /user/{userId_A}\nAuthorization: Bearer <token_for_user_B>
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthService: GET /auth\nAuthorization: Bearer <token_for_user_B>
activate AuthService
AuthService -> AuthService: Validate JWT Token
AuthService --> Gateway: 200 OK\nX-Auth-User-ID: {userId_B}
deactivate AuthService

Gateway -> UserService: GET /user/{userId_A}\nX-Auth-User-ID: {userId_B}
activate UserService
UserService -> UserService: Check X-Auth-User-ID == userId_A
note right: userId_B != userId_A
UserService --> Gateway: 403 Forbidden
deactivate UserService

Gateway --> Client: 403 Forbidden
deactivate Gateway

@enduml
